the entanglement?

00:53:28.310 --> 00:53:30.470
We are focusing
here on pure states

00:53:30.470 --> 00:53:32.390
where things are fairly simple.

00:53:32.390 --> 00:53:36.400
But in the general situation
of a many-body system,

00:53:36.400 --> 00:53:40.502
it can be quite challenging
just define and measure

00:53:40.502 --> 00:53:41.043
entanglement.

